title: Flash Back to Kevin Hart and Tiffany Haddish Interview and More
itunes:title: Flash Back to Kevin Hart and Tiffany Haddish Interview and More
description:
1/4/19- Today on the show we flashed back to the time when Kevin Hart and Tiffany Haddish stopped by and Kevin had a few things to get off his chest. Also, we flashed back to the time comedian Luenell stopped by for the first time and lets just say things got a little kinky during the show, but hey why not for freaky Friday. Also, we flashed back to when Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Nicki Minaj.
